data.description: Beautiful Home on Private Oasis lot in Tipton Co. This is a steal of a property is PRICED TO SELL! This under market value property boasts RV, Camper or Boat parking along with HUGE Shed & Above-Ground Pool in the back! This secluded home opens up to 3BEDS down along with hearth room, den & living room! Upstairs you will find a LARGE bonus room along with 2 flex spaces! Total 4BEDS/4.5BATHS, Newer roof, newer vinyl windows, NICE hardwood flooring & Central HVAC system! Schedule soon!
